{"number":13,"verseCount":14,"verses":[[1,["Let every soul ",["be subject",["study-note-ref","a",["GR be submissive, render obedience. ",["D&C 58:22 (21–22)","dc-testament/dc/58.22"],". ",["TG Citizenship","tg/citizenship"],"; ",["Governments","tg/governments"],"."]]]," unto the higher ",["powers",["study-note-ref","b",["GR authorities."]]],". For there is no ",["power",["study-note-ref","c",[["John 19:11 (10–12)","nt/john/19.11"],"."]]]," ",["but of God",["study-note-ref","d",["JST Rom. 13:1 … in the church but of God …"]]],": the ",["powers",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Governments","tg/governments"],"."]]]," that be are ordained of God."]],[2,["Whosoever therefore resisteth the power, resisteth the ordinance of God: and they that ",["resist",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Rebellion","tg/rebellion"],"."]]]," shall receive to themselves ",["damnation",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Damnation","tg/damnation"],"."]]],"."]],[3,["For rulers are not a terror to good works, but to the evil. Wilt thou then not be afraid of the ",["power",["study-note-ref","a",["GR authority."]]],"? do that which is ",["good",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Retribution","tg/retribution"],"."]]],", and thou shalt have praise of the same:"]],[4,["For he is ",["the minister",["study-note-ref","a",["GR a servant."]]]," of God to thee for good. But if thou do that which is evil, be afraid; for he beareth not the sword in vain: for he is the minister of God, a revenger to ",["execute",["clarity-word"]]," wrath upon him that doeth evil."]],[5,["Wherefore ",["ye",["clarity-word"]]," must needs be subject, not only for wrath, but also for ",["conscience",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Conscience","tg/conscience"],"."]]]," sake."]],[6,[["For",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST Rom. 13:6–7 (Appendix)","jst/jst-rom/13.6-7"],"."]]]," for this cause pay ye tribute also: for they are God’s ministers, attending continually upon this very thing."]],[7,["Render therefore to all their dues: tribute to whom tribute ",["is due;",